[SPEAKER_01] I to je dovoljno.

980
00:33:37,940 --> 00:33:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] Mi bi tijeli sigurnost.

981
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] Mi bi tijeli imat reflektor.

982
00:33:41,779 --> 00:33:43,240
[SPEAKER_01] O, kod vas dobro bi reflektor.

983
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] Mi bi tijeli imat reflektor.

984
00:33:45,759 --> 00:33:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] O, da mi cijeli život pokaži.

985
00:33:48,079 --> 00:33:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] Nije to dobro.

986
