1810
01:13:31,380 --> 01:13:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] To je od početka tako bilo.

1811
01:13:32,739 --> 01:13:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da, imamo četiri dogme.

1812
01:13:35,380 --> 01:13:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da, imamo četiri dogme.

1813
01:13:37,340 --> 01:13:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo četiri dogme.

1814
