[SPEAKER_01] Ima ovdje dio u katekizmu.

1815
01:13:40,600 --> 01:13:42,479
[SPEAKER_01] Čitajte, ljudi, katekizam.

1816
01:13:42,479 --> 01:13:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, evo i sebi to govorim.

1817
01:13:43,760 --> 01:13:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] Čitaj.

1818
