1824
01:14:03,739 --> 01:14:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to su, znamo tako, bezgrešno začeće.

1825
01:14:07,920 --> 01:14:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] Marija je bezgrešno začeta.

1826
01:14:10,840 --> 01:14:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] Začeta.

1827
01:14:12,800 --> 01:14:13,579
