1851
01:15:00,600 --> 01:15:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] oslobođena,

1852
01:15:02,159 --> 01:15:03,319
[SPEAKER_01] unaprijed,

1853
01:15:03,319 --> 01:15:04,479
[SPEAKER_01] onoga,

1854
01:15:04,479 --> 01:15:05,140
