1871
01:15:29,640 --> 01:15:32,180
[SPEAKER_01] Zato se kaže,

1872
01:15:32,180 --> 01:15:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] Isus je postao u svemu čovjeku sličan,

1873
01:15:34,659 --> 01:15:35,840
