1936
01:17:28,100 --> 01:17:30,600
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to, ta me riječ nekako dira.

1937
01:17:30,600 --> 01:17:32,619
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam došao,

1938
01:17:32,619 --> 01:17:34,560
[SPEAKER_01] evo tako, želim to reći.

1939
01:17:34,560 --> 01:17:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja doživljavam stvarno Božju pravidnost.

1940
01:17:37,760 --> 01:17:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam došao,

1941
01:17:38,460 --> 01:17:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] ne znači nisam prije doživljavao,

1942
01:17:39,920 --> 01:17:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da jesam,

1943
01:17:40,579 --> 01:17:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali sad ono što mi je najsvježije,

1944
01:17:44,560 --> 01:17:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] jednu osobu koja mi je Bog poslao

