1948
01:17:54,840 --> 01:17:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] kuhanje, pranje.

1949
01:17:56,760 --> 01:17:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Bila jedna prije gospođa

1950
01:17:59,119 --> 01:18:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] koja je odšla u mirovinu i tako.

1951
01:18:02,119 --> 01:18:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja tu doživljavam Božju brigu i pravidnost.

1952
01:18:08,560 --> 01:18:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, baš sam, baš to mogu doživjet, vidjet.

1953
01:18:11,119 --> 01:18:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] Tako vidiš

1954
